Events that occurred on 11 August
==On Earth==
</noinclude>
* '''[[1955]]''' - During a holiday to Italy, [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] and his daughter [[Priscilla Tolkien|Priscilla]] make tourism around Assisi.
* '''[[1966]]''' - [[The Christian Science Monitor (11 August 1966)|''The Christian Science Monitor'' (11 August 1966)]], including an [[Index:Interviews with J.R.R. Tolkien|interview]] with [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] by [[Daphne Castell]], is published.
* '''[[1978]]''' - [[Mythcon 9]] in [[wikipedia:West Sacramento, California|West Sacramento]], [[wikipedia:California|California]].
* '''[[1984]]''' - [[Mythcon 15]] at [[wikipedia:Mills College|Mills College]] in [[wikipedia:Oakland, California|Oakland]], [[wikipedia:California|California]].
* '''[[1986]]''' - [[Mythcon 17]] at [[wikipedia:California State University|California State University]] in [[wikipedia:Long Beach, California|Long Beach]].
* '''[[1997]]''' - [[Mythcon 28]] at [[wikipedia:Pepperdine University|Pepperdine University]] in [[wikipedia:Malibu, California|Malibu]], [[wikipedia:California|California]].
* '''[[2005]]''' - [[The Tolkien Society]]'s [[Tolkien 2005]] conference in [[wikipedia:Birmingham|Birmingham]], [[wikipedia:England|England]].
* '''[[2007]]''' - [http://omentielva.com/ Omentielva Tatya] - 2nd International Conference on [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]'s Invented Languages in [[wikipedia:Antwerp|Antwerp]], [[wikipedia:Belgium|Belgium]].
* '''[[2011]]''' - [http://omentielva.com/ Omentielva Cantea] - 4th International Conference on [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]'s Invented Languages in [[wikipedia:Valencia|Valencia]], [[wikipedia:Spain|Spain]].
* '''[[2013]]''' - [[Omentielva|Omentielva Lempea]] - 5th International Conference on [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]'s Invented Languages in Helsinki, Finland.
* '''[[2014]]''' - [[Mythcon 45]] in [[wikipedia:Wheaton College (Massachusetts)|Wheaton College]], [[wikipedia:Massachusetts|Massachusetts]].
* '''[[2015]]''' - Actor [[Richard Whiteside]] dies
* '''[[2016]]''' - Musician [[Glenn Yarbrough]] dies
* '''[[2017]]''' - [[Omentielva|Omentielva Otsea]] - the Seventh International Conference on [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]'s Invented Languages at [[wikipedia:California State University, East Bay|California State University, East Bay]].
